OL,6,FSpeaking following the decision
OL,7,FCouncillor Euan Jardine, Leader of
OL,8,FScottish Borders Council, said: "This
OL,9,Fbudget sets out a series of actions
OL,10,Fwhich will help secure the future of
OL,11,Four communities.
OL,13,F"The 10 per cent increase in council
OL,14,Ftax was an extremely difficult
OL,15,Fdecision, but ultimately members
OL,16,Facross the political spectrum agreed
OL,17,Fit was necessary to protect frontline
OL,18,Fservices and make investing in
OL,19,Fcommunities a priority."
